ectly to the oven for 5 minutes. They were very dry. I recommend marinating them beforehand. It had a great taste to them, it has potential!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/08/glazed-pork-chops/?replytocom=70083#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-70083\", \"70083\", \"respond\", \"13442\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"comment-70234\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/03272710955737656943' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Terry</a></cite> <span class=\"says\">says:</span>\t\t \t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-meta commentmetadata\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://www.budgetbytes.com/2010/08/glazed-pork-chops/#comment-70234\">10.24.12 at 5:28 pm</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-content\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<p>This will be tonights dinner! Yummmm!!</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2010/08/glazed-pork-chops/?replytocom=70234#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm(\"comment-70234\", \"70234\", \"respond\", \"13442\")'>Reply</a>\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"comment-70323\">\n\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"comment-header\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/41dc3e007986c35dc46763689fa93174?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-48 phot